ILSVRC files include the following the following files. Please use the command to unzip 
the three first-order iamge files. For the rest of the files, users can directly extract 
them into the same name files. 


1. Unzip ILSVRC2012_img_train.tar

1).Create a folder

Folder Name: ILSVRC2012_img_train

2).Unzip the first-order file 

ILSVRC2012_img_train is the first-order files. 

$ sudo tar -xvf ILSVRC2012_img_train.tar -C ./ILSVRC2012_img_train

3). Unzip the second-order files 

Users need to unzip the second-order files because the file holder of ILSVRC2012_img_train
includes 1000-classe-tar files. Please use the shell file of ilsvrc_classes_untar.sh to 
unzip the 1000 tar files. 

(1).Put the file of ilsvrc_classes_untar.sh into the fileholder of ILSVRC2012_img_train

The typical path is /media/drive/datasets/ImageNet2012/ILSVRC2012_img_train with regard to
any huge files based on the Ubuntu 18.04 guidelines. 

(2).Operate the current file holder

$ cd /media/drive/datasets/ImageNet2012/ILSVRC2012_img_train

(3).Execute the command as follows. 

With the access authority 

$ bash ilsvrc_classes_untar.sh

or 

Without the access authority 

$ sudo bash ilsvrc_classes_untar.sh


2. Unzip ILSVRC2012_img_val.tar 

The tar file does not include the second filehodlers, so users can use either the 
following command or ilsvrc_untar.sh to unzip the tar file. 

1).Create a folder

Folder Name: ILSVRC2012_img_val

2).Unzip the folder 

(1).Operate the current file holder

$ cd /media/drive/datasets/ImageNet2012/ILSVRC2012_img_val

(2).Unzip the file
$ sudo tar -xvf ILSVRC2012_img_val.tar -C ./ILSVRC2012_img_val

or 

$ bash ilsvrc_untar.sh 


3.Unzip ILSVRC2012_img_test.tar

The tar file does not include the second-order fileholers, so users can use either 
the following command or ilsvrc_untar.sh to unzip the files.

1).Create a folder

Folder Name: ILSVRC2012_img_test

2).Unzip the folder 

(1).Operate the current file holder

$ cd /media/drive/datasets/ImageNet2012/ILSVRC2012_img_val

(2).Unzip the file 

$ sudo tar -xvf ILSVRC2012_img_test.tar -C ./ILSVRC2012_img_test

or 

$ bash ilsvrc_untar.sh 



4.Unzip ILSVRC2012_bbox_train_v2.tar

User can try to unzip the file with the above-mentioned command. However, the second-order
folders are locked with lock marks. So it is convient to use the following steps to unzip
the file. 

1).Create a folder: ILSVRC2012_bbox_train_v2

2).Double click the file 

3).Extract the content to the above-mentioned folder 


5.Unzip ILSVRC2012_devkit_t12.tar

It is operated as same as the above-mentioned. 



Notes: 

ILSVRC2012_img_train.tar
ILSVRC2012_img_train
147.9G

ILSVRC2012_img_val.tar
ILSVRC2012_img_val
6.7G

ILSVRC2012_img_test.tar
ILSVRC2012_img_test
13.7G 

ILSVRC2012_bbox_train_v2.tar
ILSVRC2012_bbox_train_v2
